name: AWP | Snake Camo
description: High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. It has been spray-painted using a snakeskin stencil in patches that have been outlined freehand.

name: ★ Bayonet | Fade
description: Relatively unchanged in its design since World War II, the bayonet still retains a place in modern military strategy.
